      <description>&lt;p&gt;I don&amp;rsquo;t recall the circumstances that lead to the issue but anytime I tried to open vim for git I received:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;There was a problem with the editor vi&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The solution:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34; style=&#34;background: #ffffff&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;line-height: 125%&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  git config --global core.editor /usr/local/bin/vim
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
